  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel La Torre is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each day you can enjoy panoramic views while dining at the hotel. You'll get a continental buffet breakfast each morning and a four-course buffet dinner. The restaurant at hotel La Torre offers traditional Italian and Piedmontese dishes.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>La Torre is one of <a data-udi="umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887}" title="Sauze d'Oulx">Sauze d’Oulx's</a> most distinctive hotels thanks to its tall, <span>cylindrical shape. Its l</span>ocated just a snowballs throw away from the main streets of the resort and a great base for any skier who wants to have a good time. You don't have to wander far to find good bars, restaurants or just somewhere to sit back and relax. There's a free shuttle bus to take you to the lift, too.</p>
<h2>Convenient location</h2>
<p>The lively resort centre is just a short stroll away where you can find a variety of cosy cafes, restaurants, gift shops and vibrant bars. Getting onto the slopes is really easy, just hop on the free shuttle bus to the Clotes lift - from here you have access to the extensive <a data-udi="umb://document/342fdefebf5f411d9f973a480753767c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/342fdefebf5f411d9f973a480753767c}" title="Milky Way Ski Area">Milky Way Ski Area</a>. </p>
<h2>Facilities</h2>
<p>When you need a bit of relaxation, head over to the impressive spa located next to the hotel. For a small local fee you can access the pool, sauna, steam room and a relaxation area. There's also a small gym and massage and beauty treatments can be booked and paid for locally.</p>
<p>Before enjoying your evening meal, head to the Lounge Bar for an aperitivo and plan where you'll spend your days skiing on the Milky Way. The hotel has a wide choice of wines, whether you prefer a glass of Barolo or Gavi, there will be something to pair perfectly with your evening meal. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
